description: Reconsultation due to submission of revised plans; Demolition of existing buildings and redevelopment of the site to provide 391 residential units including affordable housing (Use Class C3) and 600 sqm of commercial floor space (Use Class B1) in new buildings ranging from 2 to 12 storey's in height, together with associated car parking, open space, landscaping and infrastructure works.
